#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"E-book viewer: Highlights panel: Show the date for highlights in the tooltip"
" when hovering over a highlight"
msgstr "电子书阅读器：高亮面板：鼠标悬停在高亮内容上时，在工具提示（Tooltip）中显示该高亮的日期"

#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid ""
"Comments editor: When changing case preserve as much text formatting as "
