#: Changelog.yaml:0
msgid "calibre-server: Fix CALIBRE_OVERRIDE_DATABASE_PATH not working"
msgstr "calibre-server：修复了环境变量 CALIBRE_OVERRIDE_DATABASE_PATH 失效的问题"

